On this scale, this upload is about 6/10.

Why didn’t anybody warn us about this “winter” thing?

REPACK: This is drawn from the bluray instead of webrips, which means better video quality in the dark indoor scenes.  The video codec is very prone to bad quality in certain kinds of dark scenes, and this season was full of those.

These copies are drawn from the highest quality sources possible, but they are encoded with lower bitrates at 360p resolution to make them ideal for the small screen - phones, tablets, laptops, and monitors.
